N:code-review
D:Review diffs, pull requests, merge requests, and patch stacks for correctness, maintainability,...
G:code-review PR-review diff-review bug-finding regression-risk security-review testing-adequacy
U[5]:
  Review a pull request, diff, merge request, or patch stack before merge
